{"tid":220100,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實學術台有唔少高質post,唔明點解有人屌無高質野睇","createTime":"2017-04-27T17:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T15:05:56.000Z","uid":148,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e691f8d271a2e8655102d801532f1e65edf802ae","tid":220100,"uid":148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:11:42.000Z","msg":"話無高質post個啲唔知你睇開咩先啱口味<br />\n學術台文、 史、 哲,連講藝術棋藝都有<br />\n呢排追緊石田佐吉三成巴打個戰國post,好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本唔係無高質post,係你地班人唔啱睇,走去5p台睇埋啲叫春扑野post就話無野睇<br />\n<br />\n以前高登學術台就話俾dse雞大學post攻佔哂<br />\n而家學術台咁多正post又唔見你地會討論<br />\n個啲咩ptgf,一日都唔洗就爆幾個post,話無高質post個班人收皮喇<br />\n根本係你地自己口味問題鐘意啲花生post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8481a630f9d4b5aea8f43db163bcc3e2c7ff99ca","tid":220100,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:13:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40108e1fe9f6416576b4cedd973f8e952341a517","tid":220100,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:13:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70d0a20330cdb4bc1aa9420b169b943b4b65c956","tid":220100,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:15:53.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得有唔少post都係好高質..<br />\n<br />\ntrue..."},{"pid":"c49449d6af3007b29ba57a372789d48c75d2b339","tid":220100,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:17:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我覺得有唔少post都係好高質..<br />\n<br />\ntrue...</blockquote><br />\n因為班人剩係鐘意啲5p花生post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a9825f405d7605ca1d3bc974ce49211135b2f0","tid":220100,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6f304e544167bc0e209bb1402571a07f1cf0bc","tid":220100,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1cf29637706bcd77f6b3c4ec281c5996db208d0","tid":220100,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:29:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話無高質post個啲唔知你睇開咩先啱口味<br />\n學術台文、 史、 哲,連講藝術棋藝都有<br />\n呢排追緊石田佐吉三成巴打個戰國post,好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本唔係無高質post,係你地班人唔啱睇,走去5p台睇埋啲叫春扑野post就話無野睇<br />\n<br />\n以前高登學術台就話俾dse雞大學post攻佔哂<br />\n而家學術台咁多正post又唔見你地會討論<br />\n個啲咩ptgf,一日都唔洗就爆幾個post,話無高質post個班人收皮喇<br />\n根本係你地自己口味問題鐘意啲花生post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不嬲都係咁架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一早講左<br />\n如果真係有咁多有心人討論學術<br />\n當初學術台就唔會大部分都係5p吹水post，因為高質學術post理論上係會推晒上頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f292512f660d18d439c24d38f0493a6580a9d81c","tid":220100,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:30:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話無高質post個啲唔知你睇開咩先啱口味<br />\n學術台文、 史、 哲,連講藝術棋藝都有<br />\n呢排追緊石田佐吉三成巴打個戰國post,好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本唔係無高質post,係你地班人唔啱睇,走去5p台睇埋啲叫春扑野post就話無野睇<br />\n<br />\n以前高登學術台就話俾dse雞大學post攻佔哂<br />\n而家學術台咁多正post又唔見你地會討論<br />\n個啲咩ptgf,一日都唔洗就爆幾個post,話無高質post個班人收皮喇<br />\n根本係你地自己口味問題鐘意啲花生post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不嬲都係咁架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一早講左<br />\n如果真係有咁多有心人討論學術<br />\n當初學術台就唔會大部分都係5p吹水post，因為高質學術post理論上係會推晒上頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過講真最好睇書，因為唔同人對歷史事件既描述都唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b03836b9027be10d1cb11bb80915e0c84762025","tid":220100,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04